Title: Global championship of driverless cars
Description: Roborace’s debut competition, which pitches multiple teams against one another with wheel-to-wheel action at events around the world. Over the course of the year, Season Alpha will experiment with different formats and challenges that will push the skills of the teams and engage with a new generation of fans.
